OL,7,FThere has been an alarming decline in
OL,8,Fcare for those with Inflammatory Bowel
OL,9,FDisease. This leads to delays in
OL,10,Ftreatment and diagnosis with sometimes
OL,11,Fserious complications: 1 in 7 adults
OL,12,Fis only diagnosed once they make
OL,13,Femergency hospital visits. Cari Davies
OL,14,Fheard from one patient who says nobody
OL,15,Ftook her seriously until she was
OL,16,Frushed into Accident and Emergency
OL,18,FWords by producer, Esme Jones
OL,20,FSophie Pearce waited 14 years to be
OL,21,Fdiagnosed with Ulcerative Colitis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
