OL,7,FDespite enduring severe symptoms,
OL,8,Fincluding losing a significant amount
OL,9,Fof blood and experiencing the urgency
OL,10,Fto use the toilet up to 30 times a
OL,11,Fday, Sophie was repeatedly told
OL,12,Fnothing was wrong. It wasn't until she
OL,13,Fhemorrhaged at home and was rushed to
OL,14,FA&E that she finally received a
OL,15,Fdiagnosis.
