OL,7,FSophie's journey with Ulcerative
OL,8,FColitis, a form of Inflammatory Bowel
OL,9,FDisease (IBD) that primarily affects
OL,10,Fthe colon and rectum, led to emergency
OL,11,Fsurgery and the removal of her bowel
OL,12,Fat age 35.
OL,14,F'I knew something was wrong... nobody
OL,15,Flistened'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
