OL,7,FDescribing her experience, Sophie
OL,8,Fsaid: "They rushed me straight
OL,9,Fthrough, took me down to theatre, did
OL,10,Fa scope, and the consultant that spoke
OL,11,Fto me as I came round from that said
OL,12,Fto me, this is the worst inflammatory
OL,13,Fbowel disease, ulcerative colitis I
OL,14,Fhave ever seen."
OL,16,FThe emergency care support worker, has
OL,17,Fsince undergone surgery to have her
OL,18,Fbowel removed, as well as a
OL,19,Fproctectomy, a procedure in which the
OL,20,Frectum and anus are permanently
OL,21,Fremoved and sealed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
