OL,7,FAn exclusive report shown to ITV News
OL,8,Ffound none of the 126 services around
OL,9,Fthe country met standards for care and
OL,10,Fstaffing for those with IBD, with a
OL,11,Fsignificant decline in the quality of
OL,12,Fcare reported by people with the
OL,13,Fdisease over the past five years.
OL,15,FOne in seven adults with IBD reported
OL,16,Fbeing diagnosed with the disease
OL,17,Fduring an emergency hospital
OL,18,Fadmission, often during long waiting
OL,19,Fperiods for diagnosis through the NHS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
