OL,7,FIBD is an auto-immune disease where
OL,8,Fthe patient's immune system mistakenly
OL,9,Fattacks the digestive tract, causing
OL,10,Finflammation and ulcers. Crohn's
OL,11,FDisease can affect any part of the
OL,12,Fgastrointestinal tract, while
OL,13,FUlcerative Colitis primarily impacts
OL,14,Fthe colon and rectum. It's a life-long
OL,15,Fillness with no cure.
OL,17,FAccording to the report, the quality
OL,18,Fof patient care has declined
OL,19,Fsignificantly since 2019, while nearly
OL,20,Fa quarter of adults reported finding
OL,21,Fit hard to cope with the disease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
