OL,7,FThe report shows that no IBD service
OL,8,Fin the UK met standards for care or
OL,9,Fstaffing with only one in five
OL,10,Fservices having enough IBD specialist
OL,11,Fnurses, often described as a
OL,12,F"lifeline" for patients with Crohn's
OL,13,Fand Colitis.
OL,15,FNurse Consultant Lisa Younge, who has
OL,16,Fworked in IBD services for 20 years,
OL,17,Ftold ITV News that she finds it
OL,18,F'frustrating' that she feels they
OL,19,Fcan't give patients the care they need.
